node.title: Man dies after serious crash in Waikato
node.description: A man has died after a single-car crash on State Highway 24, south of Matamata, early this morning.
node.content:
["A man has died after a single-car crash on State Highway 24, south of Matamata, early this morning.", "", "
\nPhoto: 123rf.com\n
", "A police spokesperson said emergency services were called to the crash about 6.30am.", "The 54-year-old died at the scene.", "Police earlier said it appeared the car had veered off SH24 and into a ditch.", "The highway is blocked and is not expected to reopen until midday, at the earliest.", "Cordons are in place at the intersections of SH24 and Te Poi Road, and SH24 and Stopford Road.", "Motorists are advised to avoid the area and to choose an alternate route."]
